      "raw_text": "smelter buildings near the north end\nof Lake Pend d'Oreille and the ma\nchinery for the plant is now being\ninstalled. The work Is being done\nunder the direction of Mr.. Wilson Of\nSpokane, an experienced smelter man,\nplant.\n\n\nMr.. Wilson reports to the officers\nOf the company that the smelter will\nbe one Of the best in the northwest.\n\n\nOres from the mines owned by the\nnew corporation in the vicinity of\nthe smelter will be treated at the\nnew plant.\n\n\nThe company will also do general\ncustom business."
